<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 21.3pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">Чтобы</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">стать</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">гимназистом, нужно</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">сдать</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">три</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">экзамена: русский, белорусский</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">и</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">математику. Наши</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">педагоги разработали</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Sitka Heading'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-language: RU;">эффективную</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica','sans-s